metadata.name: I Don't need The Moon
metadata.description:
Dedicated to the love of my life (for our 4th anniversary).

The little things in life are all she needs to be happy, and that's part of why I love her so much. She also wants so much to go see her family in Thailand (she hasn't seen them since 2017). This artwork represents both of those facts (her hand is pointing towards Thailand).


__
File size: 4800x6000 (JPEG)
- Created with Blender 3.2
